Package ezvcard

Class Summary
Ezvcard Contains helper methods for parsing/writing vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainHtmlReader Convenience chainer class for parsing HTML vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainHtmlString Convenience chainer class for parsing HTML vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainJsonReader Convenience chainer class for parsing JSON-encoded vCards (jCard).
Ezvcard.ParserChainJsonString Convenience chainer class for parsing JSON-encoded vCards (jCard).
Ezvcard.ParserChainTextReader Convenience chainer class for parsing plain text vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainTextString Convenience chainer class for parsing plain text vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainXmlDom Convenience chainer class for parsing XML vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainXmlReader Convenience chainer class for parsing XML vCards.
Ezvcard.ParserChainXmlString Convenience chainer class for parsing XML vCards.
Ezvcard.WriterChainHtml Convenience chainer class for writing HTML vCards (hCard).
Ezvcard.WriterChainJsonMulti Convenience chainer class for writing JSON-encoded vCards (jCard).
Ezvcard.WriterChainJsonSingle Convenience chainer class for writing JSON-encoded vCards (jCard).
Ezvcard.WriterChainTextMulti Convenience chainer class for writing plain text vCards
Ezvcard.WriterChainTextSingle Convenience chainer class for writing plain text vCards
Ezvcard.WriterChainXmlMulti Convenience chainer class for writing XML vCards (xCard).
Ezvcard.WriterChainXmlSingle Convenience chainer class for writing XML vCards (xCard).
VCard Represents a vCard.
VCardSubTypes Holds the parameters (aka "sub types") of a vCard Type.
 

Enum Summary
VCardVersion Contains all possible vCard versions.
 

Exception Summary
VCardException Base exception for all ez-vcard exceptions.
